import { createTheme } from "@fluentui/react"

const appTheme = createTheme({
    palette: {
        themePrimary: 'wh',
        themeLighterAlt: '#090600',
        themeLighter: '#241600',
        themeLight: '#442a00',
        themeTertiary: '#885400',
        themeSecondary: '#c87b00',
        themeDarkAlt: '#e69617',
        themeDark: '#eaa638',
        themeDarker: '#efbc69',
        neutralLighterAlt: '#262626',
        neutralLighter: '#2f2f2f',
        neutralLight: '#3d3d3d',
        neutralQuaternaryAlt: '#464646',
        neutralQuaternary: '#4d4d4d',
        neutralTertiaryAlt: '#6b6b6b',
        neutralTertiary: '#e5e5e5',
        neutralSecondary: '#eaeaea',
        neutralPrimaryAlt: '#eeeeee',
        neutralPrimary: '#d9d9d9',
        neutralDark: '#f6f6f6',
        black: '#fafafa',
        white: '#1c1c1c',
    }
})


export { appTheme }
